Merregnon: Heart of Ice - Weltpremiere Stefanie Heinzmann & MIKIs Takeover
Ensemble Stefanie Heinzmann & MIKIs Takeover Ensemble Face to Face Waseda
Symphony Orchestra Tokyo - Abschlusskonzert BASF-Festival Waseda Symphony
